\f1\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 Email me your team list with their corresponding seeds in order by seed number. Please double-check that your seed numbers are correct and that your selections total\'a0100.
\f0\b0\fs32 \

\f1\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0
