\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 Please submit your selections by tip-off Thursday, though if possible I\'92d appreciate receiving them by Wednesday evening. You can adjust your picks any time up until the first game tips.
\fs32 \

\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0
\fs32 \

\fs29\fsmilli14667 Thursday will be an extremely busy day for me because I have a guest speaker visiting my horse racing class (yes, I teach a college course on the economics of wagering markets), so I will likely not be able to send out the full spreadsheet of participants\'92 selections until late Thursday.
\fs32 \

\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0
\fs32 \

\fs29\fsmilli14667 Occasionally an email slips through the cracks, about once a year something gets caught in my spam filter, so if you submitted picks but have not heard back from me by noon Friday, please reach out and let me know.
\fs32 \

\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0
\fs32 \

\fs29\fsmilli14667 You can treat the play-in matchups as one team \'96 meaning you can take Texas/NC State for $4 and you get whichever team wins.
\fs32 \

\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0
